{"word":"G4355 - προσλαμβάνω - proslambánō - pros-lam-ban'-o - Receive","slug":"G4355","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσλαμβάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>proslambánō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pros-lam-ban'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Receive"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C3;&#x03BB;&#x03B1;&#x03BC;&#x03B2;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9; - proslambano&#x0304;</b> - <i>pros-lam-ban'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G2983\">G2983</a>; to <i>take to</i> oneself, that is, <i>use</i> (food), <i>lead</i> (aside), <i>admit</i> (to friendship or hospitality): - receive, take (unto)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1949\">G1949</a>, <a href=\"#/G2638\">G2638</a>, <a href=\"#/G2983\">G2983</a>, <a href=\"#/G3335\">G3335</a>, <a href=\"#/G3336\">G3336</a>, <a href=\"#/G353\">G353</a>, <a href=\"#/G354\">G354</a>, <a href=\"#/G3880\">G3880</a>, <a href=\"#/G423\">G423</a>, <a href=\"#/G4301\">G4301</a>, <a href=\"#/G4356\">G4356</a>, <a href=\"#/G5274\">G5274</a>"}]}